arCallbacks.szOnCallbackCompleteScript:
function Start(idActor, fRange, idActorDetector)
	if (taunt1 and PROGRESS_COUNTER == 1) then
		Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(S_CONV_BOSSBARK_1, idKeironIntro)
		Hydra.QActorPower(MortarActor, MortarPower, idActor)
		taunt1 = false
	elseif (taunt2 and PROGRESS_COUNTER == 2) then
		Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(S_CONV_BOSSBARK_2, idKeironIntro)
		Hydra.QActorPower(MortarActor, MortarPower, idActor)
		taunt2 = false
	elseif (taunt3 and PROGRESS_COUNTER == 3) then
		Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(S_CONV_BOSSBARK_3, idKeironIntro)
		Hydra.QActorPower(MortarActor, MortarPower, idActor)
		taunt3 = false
	end
end

function Start(idActor, fRange, idActorDetector)
	if PROGRESS_COUNTER >= 1 then
		Hydra.QActorPower(MortarActor, MortarPower, idActor)
	end
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)
	table.remove(tPlayersWithItem, idActorPlayer)
	if PROGRESS_COUNTER >= 1 then
		Hydra.QActorPower(MortarActor, MortarPower, idActorPlayer)
	end
	-- destroy linked blockers
	tBlockers = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActor(idActorGizmo)
	for i, idFire in ipairs(tBlockers) do
		Hydra.ActorDelete(idFire)
	end
	
--	Hydra.ActorFadeAndDelete(idActorGizmo, 3.0)
	Hydra.ActorKill(idActorGizmo)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idActorGizmo, FX_SmokeBurst)
--	Hydra.ActorKill(idActorGizmo)
	
end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	Hydra.ItemDropAtActor(idActorKilled, idTear)
	PROGRESS_COUNTER = PROGRESS_COUNTER + 1
	local tLinked = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActor(idActorKilled)
	for i, idGhost in pairs(tLinked) do
		Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(GHOST_FADEIN_POWER, "TRANS_IN", idGhost)
	end
	
end

	end

function Start(idActorLootee, idActorLooter, idActorItem)
--	local proxy = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor("Generic_Proxy", idActorLootee, true, 0, 0)
	Hydra.Wait(3)
	if #tPlayersWithItem < 1 then
		local proxy = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor("Generic_Proxy", idActorItem, true, 0, 0)
		local GHOST = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(GHOST_NPC_M, proxy, true, 1, 1, rarity, summonPower)
		Hydra.ActorAddToGroup(GHOST, "CMP_Hawe_ErimansPyre_ItemGhosts")
		Hydra.QActorFaceActor(GHOST, proxy)
		Hydra.QActorWait(GHOST, 1) 
		Hydra.QActorAnim(GHOST, "AnimKey_Point_Ground")
	end
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idItem)
	table.insert(tPlayersWithItem, idActorPlayer)
	
	local tItemGhosts = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("CMP_Hawe_ErimansPyre_ItemGhosts")
	if #tItemGhosts > 0 then
		for i, idGhost in pairs(tItemGhosts) do
			if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idGhost) then 
				Hydra.ActorFadeAndDelete(idGhost, 2)
			end
		end
	end
end

function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	tMonstersAll = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("Camp_KeironsPyre_Monsters");
	for i, actorID in ipairs(tMonstersAll) do
		Hydra.ActorKill(actorID);
	end
	Hydra.BossEncounterManuallyComplete(BOSS_ENCOUNTER_LEVEL_AREA);
	Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(CONV_PreClaim, idActorKiller)
	
	local tAllPlayers = Hydra.QuestGetParticipants()
     
    for i, idPlayer in ipairs(tAllPlayers) do
        -- Drop the TreasureClass, which contains both "always" and "first time" rewards
        -- The First Time stuff is conditioned by the flag that is set after the drop occurs
        Hydra.TreasureClassDropAtActorForPlayer(idActorKilled, "FirstTimeReward_Stronghold_ErimansPyre", idPlayer)
         
        -- Set the variable, to mark that this player has recieved a reward
        Hydra.SetPlayerVariableFlag(idPlayer, "FirstTimeReward_Stronghold_ErimansPyre")
    end
	Hydra.MusicOverride("Sanctuary_Eastern_Continent", "Music_Hawezar_Verge_Stronghold_Victory")
end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)
	Hydra.Wait(1.5)
	for i, idGhost in pairs(tPostBossGhosts) do
		Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(GHOST_FADEIN_POWER, "TRANS_IN", idGhost)
		Hydra.Wait(.5)
	end
	Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(S_CONV_ERIMAN_OUTRO_1)
	Hydra.QActorFaceActor(ClaimGhost, CampIcon)
	Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(S_CONV_ERIMAN_OUTRO_2, ClaimGhost)
	Hydra.Wait(5)
	for i, idGhost in pairs(tPostBossGhosts) do
		Hydra.ActorSetIdleAnim(idGhost, "AnimKey_Chant_Prayer_Eyelevel")
		Hydra.QActorPhasedAnimLoop(idGhost, "AnimKey_Chant_Prayer_Eyelevel_Loop", 5)
		Hydra.Wait(.5)
		Hydra.ActorFadeAndDelete(idGhost, 2)
	end
	Hydra.WaitForConversationFinished(S_CONV_ERIMAN_OUTRO_2)
	Hydra.ActorFadeAndDelete(ClaimGhost, 2)
end

	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idKeironIntro, 1)
	Hydra.ActorFadeAndDelete(ERIMAN_NPC, 1)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(PYRE_DESTR)
	Hydra.ActorDisable(PYRE_SWITCH)
end

function Start(flGameTime)
	-- emergency timeout
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idKeironIntro, 1)
	Hydra.ActorFadeAndDelete(ERIMAN_NPC, 1)
	Hydra.ActorEnable(PYRE_DESTR)
	Hydra.ActorDisable(PYRE_SWITCH)
end

function EnableGhosts(tGhostSpawners)

	for i, idSpawner in ipairs(tGhostSpawners) do
		Hydra.ActorEnable(idSpawner)
	end
	
end
szOnStartupScript:
Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(ClaimSwitch, true)
Hydra.ActorDisable(ClaimGhost)
Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(PYRE_DESTR, true)
S_GBID_PV_HAS_PLAYED_INTRO = "CAMP_Hawe_KeironsPyre_Has_Played_Intro_VO"
Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdateInActorGroup("Camp_KeironsPyre_Monsters")
PROGRESS_COUNTER = 0
taunt1 = true
taunt2 = true
taunt3 = true
INTRO_GHOST = nil
tPlayersWithItem = {}
rarity = Hydra.MR_NONE
summonPower = Hydra.PowerSNOFromName(S_GHOST_SUMMON_POWER)

local tRuneGizmos = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("CMP_Hawe_ErimansPyre_RuneGizmos");
local ambushSkeletons = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("Camp_KeironsPyre_SkeletonAmbush");

for i, idSkeleton in pairs(ambushSkeletons) do
	Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(idSkeleton, true);
	Hydra.ActorSetTargetable(idSkeleton, false);
	Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idSkeleton, false);
end

for i, idRuneGizmo in pairs(tRuneGizmos) do
	local tFires = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActor(idRuneGizmo)
	for i, idFire in pairs(tFires) do
		Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroupActorToActor(CampIcon, idRuneGizmo, "fxkit_harmless_persistentRope_fire", true, "HP_center", "HP_head")
		Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroupActorToActor(idRuneGizmo, idFire, "fxkit_harmless_persistentRope_fire", true, "HP_head")
		Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idRuneGizmo, "fxKit_damaging_persistentCast_1hand_fire", true, Hydra.ACDID_INVALID, false, "HP_head")
	end
end
